{"tid":1348210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：認同保家衛族情操　斥「黑衣暴徒」挑釁　「人哋有反應好正常」","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:57:23.000Z","uid":264683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f6efa70de83ace0d75c619c872f713284549a4","tid":1348210,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"元朗昨晚有白衣惡煞在西鐵站內群毆記者及市民，導致 45 人受傷留院。網上瘋傳短片，顯示建制派議員何君堯向一群白衣男子握手及豎起姆指，又稱「你哋係我哋嘅英雄」。何君堯今日中午開記者會指，握手片段在襲擊前拍攝，事前不知道對方會在西鐵站打人，<span style=\"color: gold;\">他又表示，當時讚對方「英雄」是認同元朗人保家衛族的作風和情操</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於大批市民被白衣人毆打，何君堯指暴力需要譴責，亦不同意「以暴易暴」，但他斥示威者將暴力事件引入全港，昨日元朗社區非常緊張，所以才有「白衣行動」。何君堯又指被襲市民是「黑衣暴徒」，「<span style=\"color: gold;\">當佢地呢班刻意來挑撥、挑釁的行為，來衝擊一個和平而寧靜的社區，人哋有反應是好正常之事</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n對於網上直播片段顯示有疑似孕婦被白衣人打至躺地。何君堯則回應指，對方也有可能被「黑衣暴徒」所傷，「都有人指黑衣暴徒打爛消防喉，四處噴水，孕婦會否因而滑倒受傷？都不知邊個打邊個。 」他強調要警方調查才知道。<br />\n<br />\n另外，被記者問到會否與白衣人「割席」，何君堯回應：「點會同人割席」，稱任何人犯法都可以原諒，但強調會同暴力割席。他強調要譴責所有暴力，若有人侵害他人身體，警方必須採取行動，他會全力支持警方的調查。<br />\n<br />\n至於對警方接報超過半小時後才到現場，何君堯說不可接受，但又指完全「不會驚奇」，正如警方一直未有採取行動管制民陣的遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%AD%96%E5%8A%83%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%9B%E6%97%8F%E6%83%85%E6%93%8D-%E6%96%A5-%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81-%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25AD%2596%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2593%258D-%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592-%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B8%25B8%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0b20cdef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25AD%2596%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2593%258D-%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592-%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B8%25B8%2F&h=e5862898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%AD%96%E5%8A%83%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%9B%E6%97%8F%E6%83%85%E6%93%8D-%E6%96%A5-%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81-%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8/</a><br />\n<br />\n死何妖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見倒你咁搞香港<br />\n咁破壞我地家園<br />\n我都好有反應呀<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你意思係咪即係可以郁你呀<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c319952772572bf2a0ea818cc1d28589683d521","tid":1348210,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"認住呢個何仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5740fd5ea7da9efe088b85c98ee5040ab38b6760","tid":1348210,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":